{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we had to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lined up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a civilian, very fat and big, with almost a jovial face, called, do you want to have [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[GERMAN] means people with the profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, knowing what [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the work was, that they had always better jobs than just perhaps digging the-- the-- you know, or building streets.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's go forward.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I pulled my father forward, and we ended up, you know, among about 25 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He asked everybody, what are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- because it-- you know, my father said something different to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was going to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I'm also a painter or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What my father said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he had already moved on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we 25 were chosen in-- as-- to go into a certain camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other 75 into a sister camp nearby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know what he was till he-- till much maybe after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew it was-- I've heard it was a foundry, and the main work was done in the other camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For us, it was mainly loading and unloading wagons of stuff, which probably the Germans had looted from somewhere, maybe Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in this camp there were people mostly-- there were-- it was the first camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had all their belongings, and very often money, and other goodies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so they did not eat what was offered, mostly the horse meat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- the-- the people, the Poles who also worked in the camp, were buying other meats and other products on the black market for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had two, three portions as-- as much as I wanted of horse meat.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
